\c 42
\s UJobe uyazithoba
\p
\v 1 UJobe waseyiphendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi:
\v 2 Ngiyazi ukuthi ungakwenza konke\x + Mat. 19.26.\x*, lokuthi kakulacebo\x + 21.27. 17.11. Zaga 1.4.\x* elingavinjelwa kuwe\x + Gen. 11.6.\x*.
\v 3 Ngubani lo ofiphaza iseluleko engelalwazi\x + 38.2.\x*? Ngakho ngikhulumile lokho ebengingakuqedisisi, izinto ezimangalisayo kakhulu kimi, ebengingazazi\x + Hlab. 131.1. Hlab. 40.5. 139.6.\x*.
\v 4 Ake uzwe, ngizakhuluma mina. Ngizakubuza, njalo wenze ngazi\x + 38.3. 40.7.\x*.
\v 5 Ngokuzwa kwendlebe ngikuzwile, kodwa khathesi ilihlo lami liyakubona\x + Hlab. 18.45.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho-ke\x + 40.4.\x* ngiya\add zi\add*nenga\x + 36.5.\x*, ngiyaphenduka ethulini\x + 30.19. Gen. 18.27.\x* lemlotheni\x + 2.8.\x*\x + 30.19. Gen. 18.27.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Kwasekusithi iN\nd kosi\nd* isikhulume lamazwi kuJobe, iN\nd kosi\nd* yathi kuElifazi umThemani\x + 2.11.\x*: Ulaka lwami luyavutha kuwe lakubangane bakho ababili, ngoba kalikhulumanga ngami okuqondileyo njengenceku yami uJobe\x + 42.8. Hlab. 5.9.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakho-ke zithatheleni amajongosi ayisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa, liye encekwini yami uJobe\x + Nani 23.1. 1 Lan. 15.26.\x*, lizinikelele umnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 1.5.\x*, njalo uJobe inceku yami uzalikhulekela; ngoba isibili ngizakwemukela ubuso bakhe\x + Gen. 20.17. Jak. 5.16.\x*, ukuze ngingenzi kini \add njengo\add*buthutha benu; ngoba kalikhulumanga ngami okuqondileyo njengenceku yami uJobe\x + 42.8. Hlab. 5.9.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho bahamba oElifazi umThemani loBilidadi umShuhi \add lo\add*Zofari umNahama, benza njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kubo; njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yemukela ubuso bukaJobe\x + 2.11.\x*.
\s Ukubusiswa kukaJobe
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasiphendula ukuthunjwa kukaJobe esekhulekele abangane bakhe\x + Hlab. 14.7. 53.6. 85.1. 126.1. Jer. 30.3,18. 31.23. 32.44. 33.7,11,26. Hez. 39.25. Hos. 6.11. Jow. 3.1. Amos 9.14.\x*; njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yengezelela konke uJobe ayelakho kuze kuphindwe kabili\x + Isa. 61.7. Isa. 40.2. Mark. 10.30. Luka 18.30.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekufika kuye bonke abafowabo labo bonke odadewabo\x + 19.13.\x*, labo bonke ababemazi mandulo, badla isinkwa laye endlini yakhe\x + 19.13.\x*, bamkhalela\x + 2.11.\x*, bamduduza ngakho konke okubi iN\nd kosi\nd* eyayimehlisele khona\x + 2.11.\x*; bamnika ngulowo lalowo uhlamvu lwemali\x + Gen. 33.19. Josh. 24.32.\x*, langulowo lalowo isongo legolide\x + Gen. 24.22.\x*.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibusisa isiphetho sikaJobe okwedlula ukuqala kwakhe\x + 8.7. Jak. 5.11.\x*; ngoba waba lezimvu ezizinkulungwane ezilitshumi lane, lamakamela azinkulungwane eziyisithupha, lezipane zenkabi eziyinkulungwane, labobabhemi abasikazi abayinkulungwane\x + 42.10. 1.3.\x*.
\v 13 Wasesiba lamadodana ayisikhombisa lamadodakazi amathathu\x + 42.10. 1.2. 2 Sam. 12.23.\x*.
\v 14 Wasebiza ibizo leyokuqala \add wathi\add* nguJemima, lebizo leyesibili \add wathi\add* nguKeziya, lebizo leyesithathu \add wathi\add* nguKereni-Hapuki.
\v 15 Njalo kakutholakalanga abesifazana abahle njengamadodakazi kaJobe elizweni lonke; loyise wawanika ilifa phakathi kwabanewabo\x + Nani 27.1-8.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Lemva kwalokho uJobe waphila iminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amane; wabona amadodana akhe, lamadodana amadodana akhe, \add kwaze kwaba\add* yizizukulwana ezine\x + Gen. 50.23. Isa. 53.10.\x*.
\v 17 UJobe wasesifa, emdala, enele ngezinsuku\x + Gen. 35.29. Gen. 25.8.\x*.
